---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import EconomicJustification from "../components/EconomicJustification.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Adidas Samba | Economic Analysis"
  description="Dedicated page for the economic framework behind Adidas Samba market behavior."
>
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="section-kicker mb-3">Section 04</p>
    <h1 class="section-title mb-4">Economic Analysis</h1>
    <p class="muted-copy max-w-3xl">
      This page isolates the theoretical and strategic interpretation of Samba's
      market performance within monopolistic competition.
    </p>
  </section>

  <EconomicJustification />

  <section class="section-shell pb-20">
    <div class="glass-card p-7 md:p-9">
      <p class="section-kicker mb-3">Key takeaway</p>
      <h2 class="section-title mb-4">Differentiation protects value in competitive markets</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
        Samba demonstrates that product identity, cultural relevance, and
        communication strategy can sustain premium pricing even when close
        substitutes exist. The economic advantage comes from perceived
        differentiation rather than technical exclusivity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
